    "name": "烦恼驿站",
    "steam_appid": 3126340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/d1edf6448c2dc600a235a8254e4a9167.avif?t=1771938006\" width=663 height=241 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>在这片世界里，生命的片段会被抽离、封存成拥有意识的书籍，供高等存在细读品尝。某日，一位地位卑微的图书管理员，邂逅了一本没有属于自己“时刻”的书。他们被命运驱使，踏上一段追寻失踪神祇的旅程。</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/cf91d2ae9eb0ef516f68a3ee5655c2ee.poster.avif?t=1771938006\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/cf91d2ae9eb0ef516f68a3ee5655c2ee.webm?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/cf91d2ae9eb0ef516f68a3ee5655c2ee.mp4?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Burden Street Station 是一款关于死胡同月台与未完故事的叙事冒险游戏。在试图理解他人痛苦的旅途中，你会成为哪一个版本的自己？</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自我之集</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改变自己，才能改变他人。特质是情绪的义肢，每一种都影响世界如何回应你，以及它认定你“应得”的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/a44655ca823e06c634f7cbea4b21b6a2.poster.avif?t=1771938006\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/a44655ca823e06c634f7cbea4b21b6a2.webm?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/a44655ca823e06c634f7cbea4b21b6a2.mp4?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘式对话</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语言会挖掘得比你想象得更深。语气温柔，他们会敞开心扉；说错话，有些东西会碎裂。有时他们颤抖，有时他们会记起完整的感觉，而你也会开始怀疑——为什么你也能感受到？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/fb12861b0b80c4f9cbbc6b95a059eab4.poster.avif?t=1771938006\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/fb12861b0b80c4f9cbbc6b95a059eab4.webm?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/fb12861b0b80c4f9cbbc6b95a059eab4.mp4?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构筑于记忆之上，而非逻辑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;洛镇、管线区、高镇——每个区域都是在慢慢腐朽的梦，其创作者早已失踪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一处，都是别人记忆中的梦境。但……你确定自己来过这里。&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/f9c2cf91ec59d7d295dfde61ff19de83.poster.avif?t=1771938006\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/f9c2cf91ec59d7d295dfde61ff19de83.webm?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/f9c2cf91ec59d7d295dfde61ff19de83.mp4?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一本没有“时刻”的书</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memo 只是勉强能容忍你——只要你能帮她，获得属于她自己的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/39b3b6a6a81e982a91a2de8c1ce186bf.poster.avif?t=1771938006\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/39b3b6a6a81e982a91a2de8c1ce186bf.webm?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/39b3b6a6a81e982a91a2de8c1ce186bf.mp4?t=1771938006\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你曾说过这些话</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创作是混乱的，终结是神圣的。你是神性与悔意之间的桥梁，不仅引导对话，更承载着某种被留下的、仍渴望被理解的东西。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras/6fe7317897b759bb260cddc52b78338f.avif?t=1771938006\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126340/extras_big/6fe7317897b759bb260cddc52b78338f.webp?t=1771938006 width=1600 height=917 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
